      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "wu Brahlſt/to Nabbagun/ka tu\nwiꞥſcham ne dohd/tad peeſauks\nwiꞥſch pahr tew to KUNGU/tad\ntas buhs tew par Grehku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Dohd wiꞥſcham labpraht/\nlaid tawa Sir̄ds fauna ne irr/kad\ntu wiꞥſcham dohd/jo ſchihſ Leetas\ndeht ſwehtihs tew tas KUNGS\ntaws Deews wiﬀa tawa Darbâ/\nun eekſch wiﬀa/pee ka tu tawu\nRohku iſſteepi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Jo tur ne truhks Nabba-\ngi tai Semmê/tadeht pawehtu\nes tew/un fakku:atiwehrdains\natwerr tawam Brahtam tawu\nRohku/kas ſpadihts tohp/un\nnabbags irr tawa Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Kad taws Brahlis weens\nEebreëris/jeb weena Eebreëru\nSeewa tew pahrdohta buhs/tad\nbuhs wiꞥſcham tew feſchus Gad-\ndus kalpoht/bet ſeptitâ Gaddâ\nbuhs tew wiꞥſcham ſiwabbadu no\ntew atlaiſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un kad tu wiꞥſcham ſiwabba-\ndu atlaid/tad ne buhs tew wiꞥſ-\ncham tukſchu atlaiſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Apdohdams apdohd wiꞥſ-\nnu no tawa gannama Pulka/no\ntawas Klehts/un no tawa Wiha-\nna-Spaida/ar ko tas KUNGS\ntaws Deews tew ſwehtijs irr/no\nta buhs tew wiꞥſcham doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un peeminnt/ka tu Kalps\neſſi bijis Egiptes-Semmê/un ka\ntas KUNGS taws Deews tew\nirr atpeſtijs/tapehz pawehtu es\ntew ſchodoen tahs Leetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Bet ja wiꞥſch uſ tew ſaz-\nzths:es ne griibnu no tew iſeet/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tapehz ka wiꞥſch teiw un tawu\nNaimmu mihto/ka tam pee tew\nlabbi klahjahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Tad nem Ihlenu/un urb\neekſch winna Auſi/pee tahm Dur-\nwim/tad buhs tam tew par Kal-\npu buht muhscham/ta patt buhs\ntew tawai Kalponei darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Laid tas tew genuhti ne\nnahkahs winnu ſiwabbadu no te-\nwim atlaiſt/jo wiꞥſch irr ka diw-\nkahrtigas Algas Algadſis tew ſe-\nfchus Gaddus kalpojs/tad ſweb-\ntihs tew tas KUNGS taws\nDeews eekſch wiﬀa/ko tu darrifi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Wiﬀu Pirindsimtibu/kas\nno taweem Wehrſcheem un A-\nwim dsem/Tehwains buhdams/\nbuhs tew tam KUNGAM ta-\nwam Deewam ſwehtiht/tew ne\nbuhs ar tawa Wehrſcha Pirin-\ndsintu ſtrahdaht/neds tawu Aw-\nju Pirindsintu zirpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Preekſch ta KUNGA ta-\nwa Deewa buhs tew tohs ikgad-\nda ehſt tai Weeta/ko tas KUNGS\nisredſehs/tew un tawam Nainam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Bet ja tam fahda Watna-\nbuhs/jepſchu tas irr titſlis/jeb\nakſs/jeb fahda zitta fauna Wat-\nna/tad tew ne buhs wiꞥſcham tam\nKUNGAM tawam Deewam\nuppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Tamâs Wahrtis buhs\ntew wiꞥſcham ehſt/tas Neſchkih-\nſtaſſtik labbi/ka tas Schkihſtaſs/\nittin ka weenu Stirnu un Breedi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Wiꞥſchu Auſini tikſat tew-\nne buhs ehſt/pee Semmes buhs-\ntew to iſleet ka Uhdeni.\n"
    }
  ],
